what should happen hereafter;
and he who reveals secrets has made known to you what will happen.

# Daniel 02:30
But as for me,
this secret is not revealed to me for any wisdom that I have more than any living,
but to the intent that the interpretation may be made known to the king,
and that you may know the thoughts of your heart.

# Daniel 02:31
``You,
O king,
saw,
and behold,
a great image.

This image,
which was mighty,
and whose brightness was excellent,
stood before you;
and its appearance was terrifying.

# Daniel 02:32
As for this image,
its head was of fine gold,
its breast and its arms of silver,
its belly and its thighs of bronze,

# Daniel 02:33
its legs of iron,
its feet part of iron and part of clay.

# Daniel 02:34
