The stone that struck the image became a great mountain and filled the whole earth.

# Daniel 02:36
``This is the dream;
and we will tell its interpretation before the king.

# Daniel 02:37
You,
O king,
are king of kings,
to whom the God of heaven has given the kingdom,
the power,
the strength,
and the glory.

# Daniel 02:38
Wherever the children of men dwell,
he has given the animals of the field and the birds of the sky into your hand,
and has made you rule over them all.

You are the head of gold.

# Daniel 02:39
``After you,
another kingdom will arise that is inferior to you;
and another third kingdom of bronze,
which will rule over all the earth.

# Daniel 02:40
The fourth kingdom will be strong as iron,
because iron breaks in pieces and subdues all things;
and as iron that crushes all these,
it will break in pieces and crush.

# Daniel 02:41
Whereas you saw the feet and toes,
